---------------
Release 1.2.0.7
---------------

This is a maintenance release for VIVIPOS Application (VIVIECR) 1.2.0.x

Previous 1.2.0.x releases may be upgraded to this release by installing the release XPI through the Add-on Manager.


------------
Dependencies
------------

This release requires VIVIPOS WebApp and WebServices Release 1.2.0.3 or above. You should also install Release 1.2.0.6 of the appropriate language pack to resolve translation-related bugs.


----------
Known bugs
----------

Bug #159:
    Application may wait indefinitely if connection to printer is lost while printing


----------
Bugs fixed
----------

Bug #307:
    Product Search by product number, barcode, or name fails in Product Management screen

Bug #309:
    Display sorting to collate no case for departments, product groups and products in the UI Display sorting to collate no case for departments, product groups and products in the UI

Bug #310
    On the table selection panel, table name should be shown in the table title section, not in the body
